<br>
This is really the best way to deal with it, both from the standpoint of keeping the special rules servers undiluted by outside influence AND from a monetary standpoint, as this way you don't tick off your current customers and you provide incentive to STAY on Legends if you do transfer there from a specil rules server. If you elect to transfer back, then your Legends experience would have just been an interesting dream you had, albeit an expensive one.<br>
<br>
I submitted this solution to them. Perhaps they will even implement it, since it does appeal to the bottom line, and all corporate entities love the bottom line.<br>
<br>
Coriolis of Erudin, Firiona Vie, Beguiler<br>
